      "sectionId": "plural",
      "title": "Plural Adjectives",
      "explanation": "In the plural, adjectives have one form for all genders: -ые/-ие. Use -ие after г, к, х, ж, ч, ш, щ. Example: большие дома (big houses), большие книги (big books), большие окна (big windows).",
      "tip": "Plural is easy — -ые or -ие for all genders!",
